lead_paragraph: Angelique Kerber, enjoying a breakout season that has her challenging for world number one, crushed 17-year-old American qualifier CiCi Bellis 6-1 6-1 to reach the fourth round of the U.S. Open on Friday.

headline.print_headline: Kerber Crushes Young Bellis to Reach Fourth Round
